item.title: Melbourne Open Research Network
item.description: Melbourne Open Research Network Melbourne Open Research Network is a collection of over 40 people, in Ecology, Bioinformatics, Psychology, Economics, Software development and more, across at least 4 institutes. You can find more about our activites by following the MORN twitter account.
